List all available controller settings:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Ctrls
List all currently available bluetooth controllers:listblue_ph.sh
View the current value of controller setting(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -g
View the current value of controller setting(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -g -r
Change the value of read-write controller setting(s) (Variable expansion disabled):printf "%8s%s\n" "" "Use the controller-specific submenus to change controller settings"
Change the value of read-write controller setting(s) (Variable expansion enabled):printf "%8s%s\n" "" "Use the controller-specific submenus to change controller settings"
Display help for controller setting(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -d
Display help for controller setting(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Ctrls -d -r
XBOX360 controllers menu:ph_show_menu XBOX360
PS3 controllers menu:ph_show_menu PS3
PS4 controllers menu:ph_show_menu PS4
AppManagement menu:ph_show_menu AppManagement
Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Advanced menu:ph_show_menu Advanced
Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Return to previous menu:return
